Package: libjournal0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: C library for writing to systemd journald without libsystemd
 libjournal implements the native journal protocol over a Unix datagram
 socket. It provides the write path to journald without linking against
 libsystemd. Thread-safe with auto-reconnect and large message support
 via memfd.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libjournal-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libjournal0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libjournal
 Header file and pkg-config metadata for developing applications that use
 libjournal.
 .
 This package contains the development headers and pkg-config file.

Package: libjournal-static
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libjournal-dev (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Static library for libjournal
 Static archive of libjournal for statically linked applications.
 .
 This package contains the static library.
